				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p>GNITS does <strong>not engage any agents or consultants</strong> for admissions. We strictly follow the guidelines prescribed by <strong>TGCHE</strong> and the <strong>Government of Telangana</strong> for the admission process.</p><p>Please <strong>do not be misled by fraudsters</strong>. The management is <strong>not responsible for any dealings made through unauthorized individuals</strong>.</p><p>If you come across any such instances, kindly report them to the college authorities at: 📞<strong> 040-29565856</strong></p>								</div>
				</div>
