				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-5d73573 elementor-position-top elementor-widget elementor-widget-image-box" data-id="5d73573" data-element_type="widget" data-settings="{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}" data-widget_type="image-box.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<div class="elementor-image-box-wrapper"><figure class="elementor-image-box-img"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1156" height="867" src="https://gnits.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/gnits-image-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-image-27948" alt="" srcset="https://gnits.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/gnits-image-2.jpg 1156w, https://gnits.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/gnits-image-2-300x225.jpg 300w, https://gnits.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/gnits-image-2-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://gnits.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/gnits-image-2-768x576.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1156px) 100vw, 1156px" /></figure><div class="elementor-image-box-content"><h4 class="elementor-image-box-title">MoU with University of North Texas</h4><p class="elementor-image-box-description">GNITS signed an MoU with the University of North Texas, Denton, USA, on October 9, 2025, marking a key step in global academic collaboration. The partnership focuses on student and faculty exchange, joint research, and international learning to empower women engineers with global exposure.




</p></div></div>				</div>
