				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p>At GNITS, research is a cornerstone of our academic philosophy, driving innovation and technological advancements. Our Research and Development (R&amp;D) Cell is a dynamic hub that fosters a strong research ecosystem, aligned with the goals of NEP 2020.</p>								</div>
				</div>
				<section class="elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-8388695 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default" data-id="8388695" data-element_type="section" data-settings="{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}">
